ortant; background: rgb(252, 252, 252) !important; max-width: 300px !important; min-width: 50px !important;\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">415</span></p></td><td nowrap=\"nowrap\" style=\"padding: 0cm 3.5pt; border-top: none; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: none; border-image: initial; width: 64px; height: 20px; vertical-align: bottom; font-size: 16px !important; background: rgb(252, 252, 252) !important; max-width: 300px !important; min-width: 50px !important;\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">575</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 20px;\"><td nowrap=\"nowrap\" style=\"padding: 0cm 3.5pt; border-top: none; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; width: 443px; height: 20px; vertical-align: bottom; font-size: 16px !important; background: rgb(252, 252, 252) !important; max-width: 300px !important; min-width: 50px !important;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">Türkiye’nin Sınır Ötesi Ticaret Endeksi Sıralaması</span></p></td><td nowrap=\"nowrap\" style=\"padding: 0cm 3.5pt; border-top: none; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: none; border-image: initial; width: 64px; height: 20px; vertical-align: bottom; font-size: 16px !important; background: rgb(252, 252, 252) !important; max-width: 300px !important; min-width: 50px !important;\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">42</span>